2011-01-28  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@lpthe.jussieu.fr>

	* include/fastjet/Error.hh (Error):
	* src/Error.cc (Error):
	  when throwing a fastjet::Error, include a backtrace of the stack
	  in the message

        * example/01-basic.cc:
